  "time_ut": 1657013036,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd4\u0db8 \u0db8\u0dc5\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db1\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The fight in the fuel queue is stopped by the sight of a dead body",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "I.O.C. A dead body calmed down the tense situation at a gas station for a while.",
        "After about three days, the fuel arrived at the IOC filling station on Bandaragama Panadura Road and a large number of customers kept their vehicles and waited in queues.",
        "The customers themselves organized themselves, numbered their vehicles according to the order they were in and waited in the queue.",
        "But by breaking all those organizational activities and encouraging various people to sneak their vehicles into the queue fraudulently from time to time, arguments took place in different parts of the queue from the beginning of giving fuel, and when some of them were about to exchange blows, the parties there themselves settled.",
        "In the meantime, a van of a flower shop in Bandaragama area was about to stop at the starting point of the queue, which caught the eyes of the majority of the people there.",
        "The driver who was there called the army soldiers guarding the fuel station and told them that there was a dead body in the van and that he had come to get fuel to take to Colombo, and the attention of everyone who was behaving restlessly turned towards the van that brought the dead body.",
        "At the same time, most of the people who were in the middle of arguments and various commotions came near the van and watched the dead body through its glass and heard the details from the driver, forgetting all the arguments that happened a little while before."
      ],
